{"tid":1157012,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解連登總係有人為屌而屌","createTime":"2019-05-16T03:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T21:37:50.000Z","uid":218353,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"60c6fdff652c9c9a72baf57ba3a007a6e473ceaa","tid":1157012,"uid":218353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:35:01.000Z","msg":"我發現總係有啲人就連個post都未睇過就直接喺下面留言屌人老母<br />\n<br />\n又有啲係睇一個兩個comment， 然後就以偏概全， 跟住又喺度屌人老母<br />\n<br />\n有一啲人仲癲， 冇原因地開post屌人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KeSq9Zq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKeSq9Zq.jpg&h=2fcae752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實咁算唔算係側面反映咗連登文化水平低下， 雖然用粗口係可以加強語氣， 但係冇原因地用粗口 就唔知想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 我諗緊佢哋所識嘅單字係咪淨係得粗口， 所以好努力咁嘗試解讀佢哋嘅粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如有人話:屌你老母弱智仔我屌你老母<br />\n我所估嘅翻譯: 大家(屌你老母)    早晨(弱智仔)    我今日好早起身啦(我屌你老母)<br />\n<br />\n主旨: 其實佢哋係為咗啲乜， 係咪平時生活壓力好大， 定係因為畀人屈得多唔敢出聲， 定係畀人欺凌， 所以先上嚟鬧人紓解壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n此post開於11:34 a.m."},{"pid":"4e19658938ff9689ba1410257f4cd77cfd01f2c9","tid":1157012,"uid":251666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:36:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab841f756a4f61e7b2744349b39b9cc56519fb8b","tid":1157012,"uid":133030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:37:01.000Z","msg":"通常係現實生活冇人理要上嚟做attention seekers"},{"pid":"912740d80c55b93ccede8457bcbe56f6f39acbe7","tid":1157012,"uid":198583,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"ci